n10 或 Win11，Win7 不行</td></tr>","+    <tr><td>DeepSeek 账号</td><td>在 <code>platform.deepseek.com</code> 注册，手机号就能注册</td></tr>","+    <tr><td>10 元人民币</td><td>DeepSeek 充值最低 10 元，能用很久（每次对话几分钱）</td></tr>","+    <tr><td>约 20 分钟</td><td>从零到能用的总时间</td></tr>","+  </table>","+","+  <div class="alert alert-warn">","+    <strong>如果电脑上有"云壳系统"或其他公司 IT 安全管理软件</strong>，可能会拦截安装或 API 请求。建议先问公司 IT：是否允许自己装 VS Code 和外部软件。","+  </div>"," </div>"," ","-<!-- Step 1 -->","-<div class="step">","-  <div class="step-num">1</div>","-  <h2>安装 Node.js <span class="badge">必须</span></h2>","-  <p>Claude Code 依赖 Node.js 运行。</p>","-  <ol>","+","+<!-- ====== S1 Node.js ====== -->","+<div class="step" id="s1">","+  <div class="step-header">","+    <span class="step-num">1</span>","+    <h2>安装 Node.js <span class="badge badge-must">必须</span></h2>","+  </div>","+","+  <p>Claude Code 需要 Node.js 才能运行。这是最底层的基础环境。</p>","+","+  <ol class="steps">","     <li>浏览器打开 <a href="https://nodejs.org" target="_blank">https://nodejs.org</a></li>","-    <li>点左边 <b>LTS</b> 按钮下载（v24.x 版本）</li>","-    <li>双击下载的 <code>.msi</code> 安装</li>","-    <li><b>关键步骤：</b>安装过程中的 "Custom Setup" 页面，确保 <b>"Add to PATH"</b> 选中（点一下选 "Will be installed on local hard drive"）</li>","-    <li>其余全部 Next，完成</li>","+    <li>点左边的 <strong>LTS</strong> 按钮（长期支持版，目前是 v24.x）<br>","+        <span class="text-muted">不要点右边的 Current 版，那是不稳定的尝鲜版</span></li>","+    <li>下载完成后得到一个 <code>node-v24.x.x-x64.msi</code> 文件，双击运行</li>","+    <li>一路 Next，但到 <strong>"Custom Setup"</strong> 页面时，注意看：","+      <ul>","+        <li>找到 <strong>"Add to PATH"</strong> 这一项</li>","+        <li>点它前面的图标，选择 <strong>"Will be installed on local hard drive"</strong></li>","+        <li>这确保 Node.js 能被系统全局识别</li>","+      </ul>","+    </li>","+    <li>其余全部 Next，Install，Finish</li>","   </ol>","-  <p><b>验证：</b>按 <code>Win+R</code>，输入 <code>cmd</code> 回车，输入：</p>","+","+  <p><strong>验证是否装好：</strong></p>","+  <ol>","+    <li>按键盘 <code>Win + R</code>，输入 <code>cmd</code>，回车</li>","+    <li>在黑色窗口输入以下命令，回车：</li>","+  </ol>","   <div class="code-block">node --version</div>","-  <p>显示 <code>v24.x.x</code> 即成功。</p>","+  <p>如果显示 <code>v24.x.x</code>（x 是数字），说明装好了。</p>","+","+  <div class="alert alert-danger">","+    <strong>如果提示 "node 不是内部或外部命令"</strong> → Node.js 没装上或没加入 PATH。<br>","+    解决：重新运行安装包，确认勾选 "Add to PATH"。装完重启电脑再试。","+  </div>"," </div>"," ","-<!-- Step 2 -->","-<div class="step">","-  <div class="step-num">2</div>","-  <h2>安装 VS Code</h2>","-  <ol>","-    <li>打开 <a href="https://code.visualstudio.com" target="_blank">https://code.visualstudio.com</a></li>","-    <li>点击 <b>"Download for Windows"</b></li>","-    <li>安装时建议勾选右键菜单选项</li>","+","+<!-- ====== S2 VS Code ====== -->","+<div class="step" id="s2">","+  <div class="step-header">","+    <span class="step-num">2</span>","+    <h2>安装 VS Code</h2>","+  </div>","+","+  <ol class="steps">","+    <li>浏览器打开 <a href="https://code.visualstudio.com" target="_blank">https://code.visualstudio.com</a></li>","+    <li>点蓝色大按钮 <strong>"Download for Windows"</strong></li>","+    <li>双击安装包，安装时建议勾选：","+      <ul>","+        <li>"Add 'Open with Code' action to Windows Explorer file context menu"</li>","+        <li>"Add 'Open with Code' action to Windows Explorer directory context menu"</li>","+      </ul>","+      这两项让你以后右键文件夹就能用 VS Code 打开。","+    </li>","+    <li>完成安装，打开 VS Code</li>","   </ol>"," </div>"," ","-<!-- Step 3 -->","-<div class="step">","-  <div class="step-num">3</div>","-  <h2>安装 Claude Code 扩展</h2>","-  <ol>","-    <li>打开 VS Code，点左侧<b>扩展图标</b>（四个方块）</li>","-    <li>搜索 <b>"Claude Code"</b></li>","-    <li>找到发布者 <b>Anthropic</b> 的，点 <b>Install</b></li>","-    <li>安装后左侧出现 Claude Code 图标</li>","+","+<!-- ====== S3 Claude Code 扩展 ====== -->","+<div class="step" id="s3">","+  <div class="step-header">","+    <span class="step-num">3</span>","+    <h2>安装 Claude Code 扩展</h2>","+  </div>","+","+  <ol class="steps">","+    <li>打开 VS Code</li>","+    <li>点击左侧竖排工具栏的 <strong>扩展图标</strong>（四个小方块叠在一起的图标）<br>","+        或者直接按键盘 <code>Ctrl + Shift + X</code></li>","+    <li>在搜索框输入：<strong>"Claude Code"</strong></li>","+    <li>找到发布者为 <strong>"Anthropic"</strong> 的那个结果，点 <strong>Install</strong>（安装）</li>","+    <li>安装完成后，左侧工具栏会出现 Claude Code 图标（一个类似 ∞ 的符号）</li>","   </ol>","+","+  <div class="alert alert-info">","+    <strong>点击 Claude Code 图标时可能会弹出 Anthropic 登录页面</strong>——先不管它，关掉。<br>","+    继续往下走，装完 CC-Switch 后���个登录页就不会再出现了。","+  </div>"," </div>"," ","-<!-- Step 4 -->","-<div class="step">","-  <div class="step-num">4</div>","-  <h2>注册 DeepSeek 并获取 API Key</h2>","-  <ol>","-    <li>打开 <a href="https://platform.deepseek.com" target="_blank">https://platform.deepseek.com</a></li>","-    <li>注册账号（手机号即可，国内直接访问）</li>","-    <li>登录后进控制台，点左侧 <b>"API Keys"</b></li>","-    <li>点 <b>"创建 API Key"</b>，命名（如 <code>claude-code</code>）</li>","-    <li><b>立即复制保存！</b>Key 只显示一次</li>","-    <li>充值（最低 10 元，非常便宜，几块钱用很久）</li>","+","+<!-- ====== S4 DeepSeek ====== -->","+<div class="step" id="s4">","+  <div class="step-header">","+    <span class="step-num">4</span>","+    <h2>注册 DeepSeek 并获取 API Key <span class="badge badge-must">必须</span></h2>","+  </div>","+","+  <p>Claude Code 需要 AI 模型才能工作。我们用 DeepSeek 替代 Claude，因为：</p>","+  <ul>","+    <li>DeepSeek 是国内公司，直接访问，不需要翻墙</li>","+    <li>价格极低，10 块钱能用很久</li>","+    <li>效果足够好，能跑全部 Claude Code 功能</li>","+  </ul>","+","+  <hr class="divider">","+","+  <h3 style="font-size:1.05rem; margin-bottom:10px;">注册与充值</h3>","+  <ol class="steps">","+    <li>浏览器打开 <a href="https://platform.deepseek.com" target="_blank">https://platform.deepseek.com</a></li>","+    <li>点右上角注册，手机号就能注册（不需要国外邮箱）</li>","+    <li>登录后进入控制台</li>","+    <li>点左侧菜单 <strong>"API Keys"</strong></li>","+    <li>点 <strong>"创建 API Key"</strong>，取个名字比如 <code>claude-code</code></li>","+    <li><strong>Key 只显示一次！立刻复制保存到记事本</strong></li>","+    <li>找到 <strong>"充值"</strong> 入口，最低充 10 元即可</li>","   </ol>","+","+  <div class="alert alert-warn">","+    <strong>Key 不要泄露给别人。</strong>它是花钱的凭证，别人拿到会用你的余额。<br>","+    Key 的格式是 <code>sk-</code> 开头的一长串字母数字。","+  </div>","+","+  <div class="alert alert-info">","+    <strong>关于模型选择：</strong>DeepSeek 新用户默认使用 V4 系列模型。<br>","+    旧模型 <code>deepseek-chat</code> 和 <code>deepseek-reasoner</code> 将于 2026-07-24 停用，不要用。","+  </div>"," </div>"," ","-<!-- Step 5 -->","-<div class="step">","-  <div class="step-num">5</div>","-  <h2>安装 CC-Switch <span class="badge">模型切换</span></h2>","-  <p>CC-Switch 是桌面工具，负责把 Claude Code 从 Claude 切换为 DeepSeek。</p>","-  <p><b>下载文件：</b><code>CC-Switch-Setup.msi</code></p>","-  <p>","-    <a href="https://github.com/farion1231/cc-switch/releases" target="_blank">GitHub Releases</a>","-    &nbsp;|&nbsp;","-    GitHub 打不开？用加速站：","-    <a href="https://gh-proxy.com/https://github.com/farion1231/cc-switch/releases" target="_blank">gh-proxy.com</a>","-  </p>","-  <p>下载后双击安装，桌面会出现图标。</p>","+","+<!-- ====== S5 CC-Switch 安装 ====== -->","+<div class="step" id="s5">","+  <div class="step-header">","+    <span class="step-num">5</span>","+    <h2>安装 CC-Switch（模型切换工具）<span class="badge badge-must">核心</span></h2>","+  </div>","+","+  <p>CC-Switch 是一个桌面工具，它做的事情很简单：<strong>让 Claude Code 不去找 Anthropic，而是去找 DeepSeek</strong>。</p>","+","+  <div class="highlight-box">","+    <strong>为什么需要它？</strong><br>","+    Claude Code 默认只能用 Claude 模型（Anthropic 公司的）。国内用不了 Anthropic。<br>","+    CC-Switch 偷偷把 Claude Code 的"后台地址"改成 DeepSeek，这样你就能用了——不需要翻墙，不需要国外信用卡。","+  </div>","+","+  <h3 style="font-size:1.05rem; margin:16px 0 10px;">下载</h3>","+  <ol class="steps">","+    <li>浏览器打开 <a href="https://github.com/farion1231/cc-switch/releases" target="_blank">https://github.com/farion1231/cc-switch/releases</a></li>","+    <li>页面会列出所有版本，<strong>看最上面第一条</strong>（最新版）</li>","+    <li>往下翻到 <strong>"Assets"</strong>（文件列表）</li>","+    <li>找到 <strong><code>CC-Switch-vX.X.X-Windows.msi</code></strong>（安装版）</li>","+    <li>点击下载</li>","+  </ol>","+","+  <div class="alert alert-info">","+    <strong>GitHub 打不开或下载很慢？</strong>用这个加速站：<br>","+    <code>https: